title: Card Data Recovery 4.6.0.0 By Katyayan
description:
Card Data Recovery for Windows is the top-ranking card data recovery tool to help Windows users recover lost data from various memory cards, mobile phones, digital cameras, USB drives, PC hard drive and other storage devices. Supports AVI, MPEG, MPG, VOB, RM/RMVB, 3GP, ASF, WMV, WMA, MP4, MP4A, MKV or FLV, etc. format.
Key features:
Recover photos, videos, music of different file formats, such as photos in BMP, GIF, TIF, TIFF, JPEG, JPG, WAV, WMV, AVI, ASF, MPEG, etc.
Restore PDF, RAR, ZIP, CHM, ISO, ICC, GDF, NTFS files and more than 300 file formats.
Supports all devices like memory cards, mobile phones, digital cameras, computer.
Recover Lost files in 3 modes: Standard Mode, Advanced Mode and Resume Mode.
Download size: 6.8 MB
System requirements:
Operating System: Windows 10/Windows 8.1/Windows 8/Windows 7/Windows Vista/Windows XP (64&32 bits) Windows Server 2012/2008/2003/2000
CPU: 1GHz (32 bit or 64 bit) or above
Hard Disk Space: 20 MB free space and above
RAM : 512MB or above
